snippet.textDisplay: He’s a massive upgrade over the clapping,Ginger. For some reason no team in the East has won the division consecutive seasons since 2003. So I expect the Cowboys to win it again in 2020. Especially how the Cowboys have been having a good year, bad year and then good year again for awhile now. I expect McCarthy to take this team to the NFC title game. Maybe even SB. I don’t know if the Cowboys will win a SB under McCarthy though. It’s been tough for SB winning coaches to win it with more than 1 team. Parcells got close to do it but fell short. Hopefully McCarthy can be the 1st to do it and not Gruden with the Raiders now.
